你能够调用以下的API:
[['FinanceInnovationSearch.find_products', {'name': 'FinanceInnovationSearch.find_products', 'description': 'This function searches for financial innovation products based on category and location.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'category', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The category of financial innovation products, e.g., financial_innovation.'}, {'name': 'location', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The location where the products are available.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'products', 'description': 'A list of up to three matching financial innovation products, each with an ID, category, and provider.'}]}], ['FinanceInnovationSearch.get_product_details', {'name': 'FinanceInnovationSearch.get_product_details', 'description': 'This function retrieves detailed information about a specific financial innovation product given its ID.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'productId', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the financial innovation product.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'details', 'description': 'Detailed information about the product, including innovation points, advantages, and terms.'}]}], ['FinanceInnovationSearch.compare_products', {'name': 'FinanceInnovationSearch.compare_products', 'description': 'This function compares multiple financial innovation products based on their IDs.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'productIds', 'type': 'ARRAY', 'description': 'An array of product IDs to compare.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'comparison', 'description': 'A comparison of the selected products, highlighting differences in innovation and benefits.'}]}], ['FinanceInnovationSearch.analyze_trends', {'name': 'FinanceInnovationSearch.analyze_trends', 'description': 'This function analyzes the trends of financial innovation products based on the category.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'productCategory', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The category of financial innovation products to analyze trends for.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'trends', 'description': 'An analysis of the trends in the specified category of financial innovation products.'}]}], ['FinanceInnovationSearch.assess_market_prospects', {'name': 'FinanceInnovationSearch.assess_market_prospects', 'description': 'This function assesses the market prospects of financial innovation products based on the category.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'productCategory', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The category of financial innovation products to assess market prospects for.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'prospects', 'description': 'An assessment of the market prospects for the specified category of financial innovation products.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `FinanceInnovationSearch.find_products` 并传入 `category` 和 `location`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "FinanceInnovationSearch.find_products",
    "args": "{'category': 'financial_innovation', 'location': 'Global'}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
